 It all started when Jay Z dropped his latest album 4:44 on Tidal. On Thursday he made it available on itunes and Apple Music which came with a bonus track. Her unexpected appearance on the album has people freaking out on Twitter after they heard her freestyle on Jay-Z’s bonus track, “Blue’s Freestyle/We family”. After making her first single with her father in 2012’s “Glory”, the five year old showed how far she has grown musically. In the track, she freestyles “Everything everything this my only single thing, Everything I hear is my answer, And if you think I say, then ?”. However, her “Boom shakalaka,Boom shakalaka” lyrics have inspired all kinds of memes to express their fascination with her rhyming game. Twitter freaked out:  To view this video please enable JavaScript, and consider upgrading to a web browser that
